00:56:47,517 --> 00:56:49,109
You can call me a stuntman as well.

1011
00:56:49,619 --> 00:56:52,144
But people call
my stunts a miracle.

1012
00:56:52,789 --> 00:56:54,757
Miracle.
- Hold on.

1013
00:56:55,225 --> 00:56:57,159
You aren't wearing a helmet either.

1014
00:56:57,761 --> 00:56:58,989
There he is.
