1546
01:26:08,944 --> 01:26:10,639
Your Honour, l went
there on a Monday..

1547
01:26:10,779 --> 01:26:14,078
..with a bowl of milk,
standing in the long queue.

1548
01:26:14,182 --> 01:26:16,514
Everyone was holding
bowl in their hands.

1549
01:26:17,385 --> 01:26:19,683
