lf every person
visiting the temple..

1575
01:27:32,427 --> 01:27:35,954
..gives the milk
to a needy instead..

1576
01:27:36,031 --> 01:27:37,794
..then they will earn more merits.

1577
01:27:37,866 --> 01:27:38,855
Right?

1578
