1633
01:30:49,958 --> 01:30:51,550
Do you have it? Any proof?

1634
01:30:54,829 --> 01:30:58,287
Your Honour..
- Mr. Kanji, the court of law..

1635
01:30:58,566 --> 01:31:00,557
